SIMPLE: unthinking
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unthinking
<hw>Un*think"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not thinking; not
heedful; thoughtless; inconsiderate; <as>as, <ex>unthinking</ex>
youth</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not indicating thought or reflection;
thoughtless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With earnest eyes, and round <qex>unthinking</qex> face,⟦br⟧
He first the snuffbox opened, then the case.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*think"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*think"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unthread</ent>⟦br⟧
